      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay i'll try running tcpdump. i'm just worried it's something more chaotic or unpredictable than just a timeout. it feels like the connection just... vanishes for no reason. \n\nis there any other way to tell if it's some kind of hardware glitch or maybe a weird intermittent interference? it's driving the dev team crazy because we can't find a pattern.",
